          <p class="caption">The Legacy of Hope Foundation is honored to have Larry King, one of our world’s most prominent media personalities, serving as an Honorary Board member. In support of the Nelson Mandela Children’s Hospital, Larry King shares his thoughts and experience when he had the opportunity to meet with Mr. Mandela in South Africa.</p>
